      • routingDriver

        public static Driver routingDriver(Iterable<URI> routingUris,
                                   AuthToken authToken,
                                   Config config)
        Try to create a bolt+routing driver from the first available address. This is wrapper for the driver(java.lang.String) method that finds the first server to respond positively.
        Parameters:
        routingUris - an Iterable of server URIs for Neo4j instances. All given URIs should have 'bolt+routing' scheme.
        authToken - authentication to use, see AuthTokens
        config - user defined configuration
        Returns:
        a new driver instance
